-- Sharp, NEC to Boost Technology Investing, Nikkei Says
-- B y   A d a m   L e
-- 2010-12-27T00:47:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-27/sharp-nec-to-boost-technology-investments-in-153-operations-nikkei-says.html
(Corrects first paragraph to say other companies are also
investing.)  Sharp Corp. , NEC Corp. and other
Japanese companies will invest a total of 530 billion yen ($6.4
billion) in environmental technologies, the Nikkei newspaper
reported.  The companies will increase their investments in 153
operations fivefold, the report said, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
